# PHProjectMapElement

**Class**

An element that represents a map within project section content.

## Declaration

```swift
class PHProjectMapElement
```

## Pinpointing the Map

- **mapType**: The type of map in the project.
- **centerCoordinate**: The coordinates of the center of the map.
- **heading**: The heading of the map.
- **pitch**: The pitch of the map.
- **altitude**: The altitude of the map.
- **annotations**: An array of optional annotations attached to the map.

## Subclassing Project Elements

- **PHProjectAssetElement**: An element that represents a media asset within project section content.
- **PHProjectTextElement**: An element that represents text within project section content.
- **PHProjectJournalEntryElement**: An element that represents a journal entry within project section content.
